            <div class="title">
                Privilege (Newspaper Article)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1947-04-16/debates/10f7b010-eb6d-4c11-8412-84864162a352/FinanceBill(Procedure)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
